---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro"
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro"
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Hedvig+Letters+Serif:opsz@12..24&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
	<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
	<title>Michael Pasimio Portfolio</title>

</head>

<body>		
	<Header />

	<div class = "hero">
		<div class="hero-textbox">
			<h3>Hi, I'm Michael.</h3>
			<p>Learning Designer, Educator, and Innovator. <br>
			I believe education is the cornerstone of a healthy, democratic society.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section>
		<div class = "focus">
			<div class="container-title">
				<h2>My Focus</h2>
				<p><em>Redefining higher education</em></p>
			</div>
			<div class="container-text">
				<p>At its core, higher education is a meeting between human lives and public institutions. </p>
				<p>Too often, this eventful meeting is reduced to a transaction. A student invests time and money; the institution provides training and a degree. Return on investment becomes the end all, be all. </p>
				<p>I believe that higher education can be something more: a public process. Universities could serve as focal points for civic participation, economic vitality, and human flourishing. </p>
				<p>	Students, guided by community organizations and businesses, could learn not just job skills but also how to understand and solve local problems. </p>
				<p>Too many universities have drifted from the communities around them, getting lost in rankings, amenities, and ROI. My goal is to put the community back in the center, working at a university that knows its neighbors, engages with their struggles, and keeps its doors open to all.</p>
					<div class="container-link">
						<a href="/projects/community-university-model">Read more >> </a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
	</section>

<!--Project Areas Section-->
<section>
	<div class="container-home">
		<div class="container-title light-blue">
			<h2>My Work</h2>
			<p><em>Three projects that show what I stand for</em></p>
		</div>
			
			<div class="container-text">
				<h2>A transformative vision</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="container-img">
				<p>I believe that education is a public good for all. Instead of forcing people to sit in on monotonous lectures while taking on thousands in debt, schools should equip people with what they need to live fulfilling lives.</p>	
			</div>
				
			<div class="container-text">
				<h2>Harnessing technology thoughtfully</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="container-img">
				<p>Rather than blindly adopting the next shiny tool, education must proactively seek the technology that help it better meet its students' and community's needs.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="container-text">
				<h2>Student Success</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="container-img">
				<p>Supporting all types of students with numerous visions of success.</p>
			</div>
	</div>
</section>
	<Footer />

	<script src="../scripts/viewport-animations.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
